```json
{
  "translations": [
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b1",
      "translation": "AIA is a trusted partner for our customers, providing them with peace of mind as they focus on financial security and family protection. Despite the profound impact of the COVID-19 pandemic,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b2",
      "translation": "I am deeply grateful to our employees, agents and partners for their adaptability in embracing new ways of working and ensuring uninterrupted support to our customers"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b3",
      "translation": "while demonstrating flexibility and dedication to their responsibilities."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b5",
      "translation": "Since the onset of the pandemic, our business teams across the Group have responded swiftly and actively worked to mitigate the impact on our communities while ensuring employee safety. The Group has"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b6",
      "translation": "implemented a comprehensive range of measures, including financial support, provision of medical supplies, complimentary coverage, access to healthcare resources, streamlined service processes and"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b7",
      "translation": "accelerated claims payments, which I am proud of. We continue to find every reason to pay claims, and during the year we paid out over USD 16 billion in insurance"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b8",
      "translation": "benefits and claims, providing our customers with critical financial protection."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b9",
      "translation": "Although measures to contain the COVID-19 pandemic resulted in new business value declining to USD 2.765 billion, as restrictions on movement eased, sales momentum turned positive,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b10",
      "translation": "and in 2021 we saw very strong momentum, with new business value in the first two months growing 15% year-on-year. Our large and growing portfolio of in-force policies"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b11",
      "translation": "generated high-quality and recurring income streams, driving a 5% increase in operating profit after tax in 2020, while free surplus generated during the period"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b12",
      "translation": "grew 7%. As at 31 December 2020, embedded value equity reached a record high of USD 67.2 billion, with the Group's local capital aggregation method coverage ratio at 374%, demonstrating"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b13",
      "translation": "our strong capital position and prudent financial management."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b14",
      "translation": "The Board recommends an increase in the 2020 final dividend of 7.5% to HKD 100.30 per share. This reflects AIA's long-standing prudent, sustainable and progressive dividend"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b15",
      "translation": "policy, enabling the Group to capture future growth opportunities while maintaining financial flexibility."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b16",
      "translation": "AIA possesses several significant competitive advantages that distinguish us in a highly competitive market. We have operated in Asia for decades, with an unparalleled"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b17",
      "translation": "platform in the region and a leading market position in most of our operating markets. Our consistent 100% focus on Asia has enabled us to capture growth opportunities across the world's"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b18",
      "translation": "most attractive life insurance region. This focus, combined with our leadership team's extensive experience in Asia and the quality of our workforce,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b19",
      "translation": "has been a key driver of our strong performance."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b20",
      "translation": "Our unparalleled distribution strength enables direct customer engagement and delivery of high-quality professional advice to help meet the substantial and growing long-term"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b21",
      "translation": "protection and savings needs of Asian consumers. Today, the public increasingly expects companies to address their needs in ways that are aligned with long-term sustainable development. AIA has a"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b22",
      "translation": "market-leading brand built on the purpose of helping people live healthier, longer, better lives."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b23",
      "translation": "We aim to position AIA as a global leader in technology application, enhancing connectivity, scaling and improving efficiency. Deeper insights from data analytics help"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b24",
      "translation": "us create unique and personalized customer experiences. Products and services that are tailored to and reflect individual needs and lifestyles have transformed how people view life insurance,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b25",
      "translation": "establishing a solid foundation for building long-term relationships with our customers."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b26",
      "translation": "Although 2020 was an unprecedented year, I am more optimistic than ever about the prospects for the Asian life insurance industry and the future of AIA. We continue to challenge ourselves,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b27",
      "translation": "develop our strategic priorities and ensure we continue to appropriately address the evolving expectations and financial needs of our customers. Our new corporate strategy builds on"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b28",
      "translation": "AIA's existing strengths and advances our transformation to deliver the best service to our customers in the future."
    }
  ]
}
```
